@ParagonDS , I have watched many of our videos over the past few months, especially as I was going through my second and now third DS3 play-through; And I must say that this was, in my opinion, a very accurate breakdown of dark souls 3. The points you mentioned about PVP class builds being limited due to lack of quality variety were justified and noticed. Many discussions that you brought up within this video, I can relate to and agree with. Dark Souls 3 imo was one of the, if not the best game in the souls/borne franchise. 

I have recently subscribed to this channel, and have decided to actively continue watching your videos. This was a stellar review, nothing to it. You gave your rounded opinion on the game and I respect that. I hope you will continue to play dark souls 3 moving forward, as well as make more souls series videos. If in the rare chance that you have read this, I wanted to say thank you for being you, and providing this community such great content.

Have an excellent day - Enraged Mongoose
